Package com.saicone.types

Class TypeOf<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.saicone.types.TypeOf<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the defined annotated type in this object.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypeParser<T>
    public abstract class TypeOf<T>
extends Object
implements TypeParser<T>
    Represents an automatic detection type parser that retrieves the provided type parameter at runtime.
    This object also has methods to interact along with annotated type.
